8">哈利·斯泰尔斯七月份在奥地利举行的音乐会上也被击中眼睛</a>。</p><p>此后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-nas-x">Lil Nas X</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-nas-x-pauses-gig-after-fan-throws-sex-toy-on-stage-3464509">短暂停止了在斯德哥尔摩的一场演出，以应对人造性玩具意外出现在舞台上的情况</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bebe-rexha-reveals-facial-injuries-after-having-phone-thrown-at-her-attacker-arrested-3458053">Bebe Rexha 在纽约一场演出中被手机击中脸部后需要缝针</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/steve-lacy-smashes-fans-phone-and-storms-offstage-during-new-orleans-concert-3335765">史蒂夫·莱西选择粉碎扔向他的一个</a>。</p><p>许多其他艺术家也呼吁音乐会观众停止在舞台上扔东西，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-calls-on-fans-to-stop-throwing-things-at-artists-on-stage-3464740">阿黛尔</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-warns-fans-against-throwing-things-onstage-at-las-vegas-residency-3476190">凯莉·克拉克森</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/latto-says-someone-will-get-their-ass-beat-if-a-fan-threw-something-at-her-again-3469364-3469364">拉托</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-fans-throwing-objects-at-performers-is-infuriating-3468291">将这种趋势描述为“令人愤怒”</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">Slipknot</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists-corey-taylor">Corey Taylor</a>则表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-on-fans-throwing-things-at-performers-artists-arent-regarded-as-people-anymore-3479191">“艺术家不再被视为人”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/florence-pugh-gets-hit-in-the-eye-by-object-thrown-at-ccxp-2023-3552516">弗洛伦斯·普 (Florence Pugh) 在 CCXP 2023 上被投掷物击中眼睛的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
